text: National Highway 126A, commonly referred to as NH 126A is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 26. NH-126A runs in the state of Odisha in India. == Route == NH126A connects Barapali, Rampur, Singhijuba, Bisalpalii, Nagapalli and Sonepur in the state of Odisha. == Junctions == : Terminal near Barapali. : Terminal near Sonapur. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 126A on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Odisha
